  <name>ColorWall</name>
  <summary>The Ultimate Desktop Wallpaper Application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>ColorWall is a powerful desktop wallpaper store, manager, downloader, and application that provides users with a vast selection of high-quality wallpapers to choose from.</p>
    <p>Key features of ColorWall:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Comprehensive search: search using Colors, Tags, Categories, Resolution, Popularity, Views...</li>
      <li>Large collection of Wallpapers: boasts the world's largest collection of online 4k, 8k and Ultra HD wallpapers</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support/Multiple backend support: windows, cinnamon, deepin, lxqt, mate, pantheon, kde-plasma-5, unity, xfce4, and even FEH and WAL</li>
      <li>Highly optimized browsing experience: infinity-scrollable wallpaper browsing viewport</li>
      <li>Built-in Image viewer: preview wallpapers before downloading them</li>
      <li>Multithreaded download manager: download multiple wallpapers simultaneously</li>
      <li>Smart multiple wallpaper selection mode: select multiple wallpapers you want to download at once</li>
      <li>Smart Image metadata extraction: extracts Dominant color, Subject/Theme of wallpaper</li>
      <li>Content filtering: including an powerful age filter,to filter wallpaper search</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
